  "title": "Assistant Technician (Steel Fibre) #74827",
  "description": "<p><strong>Job Description</strong></p><ul><li>Industry/ Organization Type: Manufacturing</li><li>Position Title: <strong>Assistant Technician (Steel Fibre)</strong></li><li>Working Location: Gul Circle (6 minutes walk from CR24 MRT)</li><li>Working Hours: 5.5 days (Mon-Fri 8am-5pm, Sat 8am-12pm)</li><li>Salary Package: <strong>Basic Salary $2,500 + VB</strong></li><li>Duration: Permanent</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p><ul><li>Operate equipment to draw steel wire and produce steel fibers.</li><li>Maximize efficiency by optimizing raw materials and consumables like wire rods, dies, and lubricants.</li><li>Help prepare Manufacturing Procedure Specifications (MPS) and Quality Control Plans (QCP) for different products.</li><li>Assist in developing a Maintenance Plan for the facility.</li><li>Support product testing and identify necessary changes to meet product standards.</li><li>Maintain and replenish raw material and consumable supplies to ensure ongoing production.</li><li>Collaborate with the sales team to align delivery requirements with production capacity.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>APPLY NOW!!!</strong></p><ul><li>Completion of Secondary 4, GCE ‘N’ or ‘O’ levels, or ITE in Engineering (Electrical, Mechanical, or Mechatronics) is preferred.</li><li>Familiar with operating and maintaining machinery.</li><li>Knowledge of wire drawing consumables like dies and lubricants.</li><li>Experience with steel wire drawing equipment and butt welding equipment for joining wires is a plus.</li><li></li></ul><p>Kindly apply through <strong>ANY </strong>of the following methods:</p><ul><li>Submit your application by clicking the <strong>APPLY </strong>button;</li><li>Email your resume to <a href=\"mailto:Job@anradus.com.sg\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\">Job@anradus.com.sg</a>. Please indicate <strong>#74827 </strong>on the email subject.</li><li></li></ul><p><strong>Anradus Application Policy:</strong> We value each application and ensure every resume is reviewed. Our process is efficient, typically concluding within <strong>3 working days</strong>. If you do not receive communication from us within this timeframe, it's likely that your application has not been shortlisted by our client. In such cases, we recommend continuing your job search to maximize your opportunities.</p><p><br /><br /></p><p>Anradus Pte Ltd | EA License No. 20C0161 | Rachael Lee | EA Reg No.: R2093131</p>",
